Document: TriangleMesh  
Path: godot/classes/class_trianglemesh.rst  
Summary: Creates a bounding volume hierarchy (BVH) tree for triangle geometry to enable efficient intersection queries without a physics engine.  

TriangleMesh creates a bounding volume hierarchy (BVH) tree structure around triangle geometry. The BVH tree can be used for efficient intersection queries without involving a physics engine. For example, this can be used in editor tools to select objects with complex shapes based on the mouse cursor position. Note: Creating the BVH tree for complex geometry is a slow process and best done in a background thread.
